response.overview: The Original Misfits' Coachella Weekend 1 performance was a unique and energetic experience, blending nostalgia with a defiant, almost out-of-place, vibe. Glenn Danzig's presence brought a unique tension to the set, and the band's performance was a blend of hit songs and deep cuts from their early catalog.  Setlist: Death Comes Ripping I Turned Into a Martian Vampira Where Eagles Dare Some Kinda Hate Hybrid Moments Bullet Mommy, Can I Go Out and Kill Tonight? Hollywood Babylon London Dungeon Earth A.D. Green Hell Come Back Horror Business (preceded by band introduction) Violent World Halloween Skulls Astro Zombies Last Caress
response.title: Misifits - Coachella Weekend 1
